    <y>71</y>
    <width>541</width>
    <height>140</height>
    <text>Every widget has properties "x", "y", "width", "height"
that define its position within the display.

Every widget also has a "name" that can be used to identify a widget.

Many widgets have a "foreground_color" or "font".</text>
